Step 2: Explore the Interface
Identify key interface components:

Tactics (columns): Adversary goals like Initial Access, Execution, Persistence
Techniques (cells): Specific attack methods within each tactic
Sub-techniques: Expandable details under main techniques
Layer controls: Top menu for customization
