Task 3: Analyze Defense Gaps
Step 1: Create Defense Coverage Layer
In Navigator, create a new layer: "Defense-Coverage"

Map your current defensive capabilities against APT29 techniques using this scoring:

Score 3 (Green): Strong defense with detection and prevention
Score 2 (Yellow): Partial defense with limited visibility
Score 1 (Red): Weak or no defense coverage
Example defense mapping:

T1566.001: Score 2 (Email filtering exists, limited sandboxing)
T1059.001: Score 1 (Basic logging only, no behavioral detection)
T1078.004: Score 3 (Strong MFA and cloud monitoring)
Save as defense-coverage.json
