Troubleshooting Tips
Navigator won't start:

Check if port 4200 is already in use: lsof -i :4200
Kill existing process: pkill -f angular
Restart: npm start
Script import errors:

Verify Python version: python3 --version (should be 3.10+)
Install missing modules: pip3 install <module_name>
JSON file errors:

Validate JSON syntax: python3 -m json.tool < file.json
Check file permissions: ls -la *.json
Ensure proper file paths in scripts
Layer won't load in Navigator:

Verify JSON structure matches Navigator format
Check that "versions" field is present
Ensure "techniques" is a list, not empty
